(ns dpham.cv.components.drawer
  (:require
   [dpham.cv.components.core :refer [custom-theme cs with-styles mui-list-item]]
   [dpham.cv.components.colors :as colors]
   [clojure.string :as str]
   [reagent.core :as reagent]
   [re-frame.core :as rf :refer [dispatch subscribe]]
   [goog.object :as gobj]

   ["@material-ui/core" :as mui]
   ["@material-ui/icons/AttachMoney" :default ic-attach-money]
   ["@material-ui/icons/BarChart" :default ic-bar-chart]
   ["@material-ui/icons/ChevronLeft" :default ic-chevron-left]
   ["@material-ui/icons/ChevronRight" :default ic-chevron-right]
   ["@material-ui/icons/ExpandMore" :default ic-expand-more]
   ["@material-ui/icons/ExpandLess" :default ic-expand-less]
   ["@material-ui/icons/Forum" :default ic-forum]
   ["@material-ui/icons/Dashboard" :default ic-dashboard]
   ["@material-ui/icons/Explore" :default ic-explore]
   ["@material-ui/icons/Home" :default ic-home]
   ["@material-ui/icons/Layers" :default ic-layers]
   ["@material-ui/icons/Note" :default ic-note]
   ["@material-ui/icons/People" :default ic-people]
   ["@material-ui/icons/Public" :default ic-public]
   ["@material-ui/icons/Settings" :default ic-settings]
   ["@material-ui/icons/ShoppingCart" :default ic-shopping-cart]
   ["@material-ui/icons/TrendingUp" :default ic-trending-up]
   ["@material-ui/icons/ZoomIn" :default ic-zoom-in]))

(defn drawer-style [theme]
  (let [drawer-width 240
        transitions (.-transitions theme)
        duration (.-duration transitions)
        easing-sharpe (.. transitions -easing -sharp)
        spacing-unit (.. theme -spacing -unit)
        breakpoint-sm-up ((.. theme -breakpoints -up) "sm")]

    #js {:drawerPaper
         #js {:position "relative"
              :white-space "nowrap"
              :width drawer-width
              :transition
              (.create transitions "width"
                       #js {:easing easing-sharpe
                            :duration (.-enteringScreen duration)})}

         :drawerPaperClose
         #js {:paper #js {:background (.. theme -palette -primary -main)
                          :color (.. theme -palette -common -white)}
              :overFlowX "hidden"
              :position "relative"
              :transition
              (.create transitions "width"
                       #js {:easing easing-sharpe
                            :duration (.-leavingScreen duration)})
              :width (* spacing-unit 8)
              "@media (min-width:600px)"
              #js {:width (* spacing-unit 9)}}

         :toolbarIcon (.assign js/Object
                               (.. theme -mixins -toolbar)
                               #js {:display "flex"
                                    :align-items "center"
                                    :justify-content "flex-end"
                                    :padding "0px 8px"
                                    :width "100%"})
         :divider #js {:background-color "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12)"}}))

(defn list-divider [classes]
  (let [divider-class (cs (gobj/get classes "divider"))]
    [:> mui/Divider {:class divider-class}]))

(defn mui-list-item-root [[icon text] & {:keys [dispatch-event style open?]}]
  [:> mui/ListItem {:button true
                    :on-click (when dispatch-event #(rf/dispatch dispatch-event))
                    :style style}
   (when icon [:> mui/ListItemIcon {:style {:padding-left "8px"}}
               [:> icon {:style {:color "white"}}]])
   [:> mui/ListItemText {:primaryTypographyProps #js {:style #js {:color "white"}}
                         :primary text}]
   [:> (if open? ic-expand-less ic-expand-more)]])

(defn mui-list-item-nested [[icon text] & {:keys [dispatch-event style]}]
  [mui-list-item [icon text]
   :dispatch-event dispatch-event
   :style (merge {:background-color (colors/colors-rgb :darkorange)} style)])

#_(defn tabs [displayed-sublist classes]
  [:<>
   [list-divider classes]
   [mui-list-item [ic-explore "Summary"]
    :dispatch-event [:set-active-panel :dashboard]]
   [mui-list-item [ic-bar-chart "Work"]
    :dispatch-event [:set-active-panel :work]]
   [mui-list-item [ic-dashboard "Education"]
    :dispatch-event [:set-active-panel :education]]
   [mui-list-item-root [ic-dashboard "Skills"]
    :dispatch-event [:ui-states/toggle-drawer-sublist ::skills]
    :open? (contains? displayed-sublist ::skills)]
   [:> mui/Collapse {:in (contains? displayed-sublist ::skills)}
    [mui-list-item-nested [ic-public "Statistics"]
     :dispatch-event [:set-active-panel :statistics-skills]]
    [mui-list-item-nested [ic-attach-money "Programming"]
     :dispatch-event [:set-active-panel :programming-skills]]]])

(defn tabs [displayed-sublist classes]
  [:<> #_[list-divider classes]
   [mui-list-item [ic-explore "Summary"]
    :dispatch-event [:set-active-panel :dashboard]]
   [mui-list-item [ic-bar-chart "Work"]
    :dispatch-event [:set-active-panel :work]]
   [mui-list-item [ic-dashboard "Education"]
    :dispatch-event [:set-active-panel :education]]])

(defn drawer-react [{:keys [classes] :as props}]
  (let [drawer-open? (subscribe [:ui-states/drawer-open?])
        sublist-displayed (subscribe [:ui-states/drawer-displayed-sublists])]
    (fn [{:keys [classes] :as props}]
        [:> mui/Drawer
         {:variant "permanent"
          :open @drawer-open?
          :class (cs (.-drawerPaper classes)
                     (when-not @drawer-open? (.-drawerPaperClose classes)))
          :ModalProps #js {:onBackdropClick #(dispatch [:ui-states/toggle-drawer])}
          :PaperProps #js {:style #js
                           {:background (.. custom-theme -palette -primary -main)
                            :color (.. custom-theme -palette -common -white)
                            :position "relative" :overflowX "hidden"}}}
         [:div {:style {:width "240px"}}
          [:div {:class (.-toolbarIcon classes)}
           [:> mui/IconButton {:onClick #(dispatch [:ui-states/toggle-drawer])}
            [:> ic-chevron-left {:style {:color "white"}}]]]
          [list-divider classes]
          [:> mui/List [tabs @sublist-displayed classes]
           #_[tabs @sublist-displayed classes]]]])))

(def drawer (with-styles [drawer-style] drawer-react))
